      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Sharp pain that moves, especially to the lower right side, needs to be evaluated by a medical professional as it could indicate something serious like appendicitis. Do not take extra-strength NSAIDs or any prescription opioids without first consulting a doctor, as this could mask symptoms that require immediate attention. For now, try resting in a comfortable position and consider a warm compress on your abdomen. If the pain worsens or you develop a fever, seek urgent medical care right away.",
