      "content": "Please understand that intense, shifting abdominal pain should not be dismissed as mere cramps, regardless of the time or cost. Taking opioids like Oxycodone to sleep through potentially serious abdominal pain could be dangerous and mask critical symptoms. Since you are in significant pain, try over-the-counter antispasmodics first, but if the pain persists or escalates, you must get professional medical advice immediately. Do not self-medicate with strong prescription narcotics in this situation.",
