      "role": "user",
      "content": "antispasmodics? ugh okay. i already tried some buscopan earlier and it didnt really do much. honestly i'm just so tired i can't even think straight. if i promise to keep an eye on it and only take like half a pill of the oxy, is that still a bad idea? i just feel like i'm overreacting and i really just need to rest. what's the worst that could happen if it's just gas?",
